      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo, featuring the legendary 2JZ-GTE inline-six with factory-spec sequential twin-turbochargers. This example retains its original Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission and Torsen limited-slip differential. The chassis remains exceptionally rigid, benefiting from the factory-engineered double-wishbone suspension and 4-piston front calipers. Recent leak-down and compression tests yield optimal results across all cylinders. Finished in flawless Renaissance Red with a pristine black leather cockpit, this A80 remains in its stock configuration, free from aftermarket modifications or structural fatigue. A rare opportunity for the discerning collector seeking mechanical perfection.",
