      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector-grade example, maintained to a standard rarely seen outside a showroom. The exterior retains its deep, mirror-like factory finish, entirely free of swirls, chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin is immaculate; the premium leather remains supple and unmarked, still carrying that distinct factory-fresh scent. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced climate control, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, backed by a comprehensive service history documenting every scheduled maintenance and inspection performed by certified specialists. The undercarriage is as pristine as the bodywork, reflecting a life spent exclusively in a climate-controlled garage. This is a meticulously preserved piece of automotive engineering, offered with all original keys, manuals, and a clean title. It is, quite simply, indistinguishable from new.",
